	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Can someone give me real good manuals for GB(C) programming using <strong><span style="text-decoration: underline">assembler</span></strong>. I'm not sure of using C, I mean yeah it's simple, but performance is getting lower.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
